This is a proof of concept project created by <a href="http://twitter.com/thegreengrass" target="_blank">@thegreengrass</a> with massive help from <a href="http://twitter.com/banderkat" target="_blank">@banderkat</a> and <a href="http://twitter.com/dstys" target="_blank">@dstys</a>, none of whom are in any way affiliated with PATCO or DRPA.
</div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0 0 1em;">
